<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870526-0043 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:International Totalizator Systems Inc.</HL><DD> 05/26/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS ITSI </IN><DATELINE> INTERNATIONAL TOTALIZATOR SYSTEMS INC. (San Diego)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    SirMichael G. R. Sandberg was named a director of this maker ofcomputerized wagering equipment, succeeding Kenneth Tiede,who resigned &quot;for personal reasons,&quot; a company spokesmansaid. Mr. Sandberg retired as chairman and chief executiveofficer of Hong Kong-based Hong Kong andamp; Shanghai Banking Corp.late last year, International Totalizator said. Mr. Tiedecouldn't be reached for comment.</TEXT></DOC>